(2, 'vi_VN', 'Viva Flip Caso Sheen Collection for iPhone 4', 'viva flip caso sheen collection for iphone 4 , ', '', '&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-style-span&quot; style=&quot;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;- Viva Flip Caso &lt;span style=&quot;color:#f00;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sheen&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt; Collection for iPhone 4 l&amp;agrave; mẫu thiết kế mới nhất của Viva Madrid.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Arial,Verdana,sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;- Chất liệu b&amp;ecirc;n trong được l&amp;agrave;m từ kim loại , gi&amp;uacute;p tạo n&amp;ecirc;n vẻ đẹp mạnh mẽ, chắc chắn cho d&amp;ograve;ng sản phẩm &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-style-span&quot; style=&quot;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#f00;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sheen&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Arial,Verdana,sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-style-span&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hps&quot; title=&quot;Nhấp để xem bản dịch thay thế&quot;&gt;C&amp;aacute;c t&amp;iacute;nh năng&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span title=&quot;Nhấp để xem bản dịch thay thế&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial,Verdana,sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-style-span&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;+ V&lt;span class=&quot;hp